      @Experimental <T> void redirect(IBlockComponentProvider provider, Class<T> clazz, int priority)
      Registers an IBlockComponentProvider instance to allow redirecting the object being displayed. A BlockEntity is also an acceptable class type.
      Parameters:
      provider - the data provider instance
      clazz - the highest level class to apply to
      priority - the priority of this provider 0 is the minimum, lower number will be called first
      See Also:
